    <item>
      <title>特朗普支持共和党众议院保守派领袖鲍勃·古德的对手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/trump-endorses-gop-opponent-of-top-house-conservative-bob-good</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普周二支持众议员鲍勃·古德的初选对手，古德是国会中最保守的共和党人之一，也是众议院自由党团主席。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/trump-endorses-gop-opponent-of-top-house-conservative-bob-good</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 00:17:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普检察官敦促对封口费阴谋和掩盖事实定罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/trump-prosecutor-urges-conviction-over-hush-money-plot-cover-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普封口费案的一名检察官敦促纽约陪审团考虑“大量”证据，这些证据表明这位前总统曾试图通过向一名成人电影明星付钱让他对所谓的性接触保持沉默，然后试图掩盖他的踪迹，以影响 2016 年大选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/trump-prosecutor-urges-conviction-over-hush-money-plot-cover-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 00:07:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平会见阿拉伯领导人，中国与中东关系超越贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/xi-hosts-arab-leaders-as-china-mideast-ties-widen-beyond-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，习近平主席将会见阿拉伯领导人，寻求加深与该地区中国大量开展商业往来和外交往来的联系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/xi-hosts-arab-leaders-as-china-mideast-ties-widen-beyond-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉禁止欧盟监督员参与七月总统选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/venezuela-bars-eu-monitors-from-july-presidential-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉撤回了对欧盟选举监督员的邀请，这降低了国际社会接受7月份总统选举结果的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/venezuela-bars-eu-monitors-from-july-presidential-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 22:09:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平承诺将把青年就业作为首要政策重点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/china-s-xi-pledges-to-make-youth-employment-a-top-priority</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平在 7 月份的一次重要政策会议上承诺优先考虑青年就业问题，并投入更多资源创造就业机会，这增强了人们对该领域改革的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/china-s-xi-pledges-to-make-youth-employment-a-top-priority</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 11:00:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
